Package chocAn

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BillingVerify
    This class verifies member and service information as well as records information of a service.
    EftData
    class to handle EFT Data for the sake of keeping a record of what each provider must be paid for the week
    GenerateReports
    helper class that contains methods for generating Member, Provider, Summary, and EftData reports
    Interface
    This class is the main interface which is used to interact with the ChocAn database
    Manage
    This class is the main manage class.
    ManagerInterface
    helper class that contains methods to prompt the user as well as allowing them to request reports
    Member
    Entity class that contains information for members.
    MemberReport
    Boundary Class that gathers and outputs information needed for member reports
    OperatorInterface
    This class allows access to the operator interface, which allows members and providers to be managed
    Provider
    Entity class that contains information for providers.
    ProviderDirectory
    This class writes the Provider Directory from a csv file to 2 arrays containing the service codes and service names.
    ProviderInterface
    This class is the interface providers will interact with.
    ProviderReport
    Boundary Class that gathers and outputs information needed for provider reports
    Report
    Abstract class for other reports
    RequestProviderDirectory
    This class returns the provider directory.
    Service
    Entity class that contains information for service records.
    SummaryReport
    Boundary Class that gathers and outputs information needed for summary reports
